sentence: At the time of his death Sherrington received honoris causa Doctors from twenty-two universities: Oxford, University of Paris, Manchester, University of Strasbourg, Louvain, Uppsala University, Lyon, Eötvös Loránd University, National and Kapodistrian University of Athens, University of London, University of Toronto, Harvard, Dublin, Edinburgh, Montreal, Liverpool, Brussels, Sheffield, University of Bern, Birmingham, Glasgow, and the University of Wales.
